"""Streebog (GOST R 34.11-2012) MDS matrix and round constants.

_streebog_a_rows: 64x8 MDS matrix for the L linear transform.
_round_key_byte: 12 x 64-byte round constants C[0..11].
_get_round_constant: assembles a full 64-byte round constant from _round_key_byte.
"""

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# A (linear transform L) rows — GOST R 34.11-2012, §5.2.3
# 64x8 matrix; each row is 8 bytes (one output column of the MDS transform).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

fn _streebog_a_rows() -> [[u8]]:
